snippet: Karrie Webb of Australia shot a two-under-par 70 to take a one-stroke lead over Angela Stanford of the United States through the third round of the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore.
abstract: Karrie Webb takes third-round lead at HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Karrie Webb of Australia shot a two-under-par 70 to take a one-stroke lead over Angela Stanford of the United States through the third round of the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore.
